@startuml sequence_production_signin
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Production Sign-In (Entra ID) with JIT User Upsert

actor "End User" as User
participant "Angular SPA" as SPA
participant "Entra ID" as Entra
participant "JwtBearer\nMiddleware" as JWT
participant "UserBootstrap\nHandler" as Boot
participant "IUserRepository" as Repo
participant "ICurrentUser" as CU
participant "MediatR\nHandler" as MR
database "user table" as DB

User -> SPA: Open app
SPA -> Entra: Authorization Code + PKCE
Entra --> SPA: id_token + access_token
SPA -> JWT: GET /api/tree\nAuthorization: Bearer <jwt>
JWT -> JWT: Validate issuer / signature\naudience / expiry (L2-022)
JWT -> Boot: OnTokenValidated(principal)
Boot -> Boot: Read email claim\n(fail if missing)
Boot -> Repo: FindByEmailAsync(email)
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM user
DB --> Repo: null
Repo --> Boot: null
Boot -> Repo: CreateAsync(email, hash=null)
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO user(email, ...)
DB --> Repo: User { Id }
Repo --> Boot: User
Boot -> CU: Set UserId, Email
Boot --> JWT: ok
JWT -> MR: Invoke handler
MR --> SPA: 200 OK { tree }

@enduml
